SUMMARY:Azure Decoded: Kickstart AI Security with Microsoft Defender for C
 loud
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nStart your journey to secure AI wor
 kloads in the cloud. Learn how Defender for Cloud provides foundational pr
 otection for your AI solutions and why it’s essential for modern securit
 y strategies.\n\n**What you’ll learn:**\n- Identify the layers that make
  up AI workloads in Azure\n- Recognize security risks unique to AI\, inclu
 ding prompt injection\, data leakage\, and model misuse\n- Explain how Mic
 rosoft Foundry provides guardrails and observability for AI models\n- Desc
 ribe how Microsoft Defender for Cloud\, Microsoft Purview\, and Microsoft 
 Entra ID work together to secure and govern AI workloads\n- Summarize how 
 these services align to create a unified\, defense-in-depth strategy for A
 I security in Azure\n\n**Who should attend:** Developers\, Security Engine
 ers\, and technical professionals who want to learn how Defender for Cloud
  provides foundational protection for AI solutions and why it’s essentia
 l for modern security strategies.\n\n-------------------------------------
 ------------------\n[Enable threat protection for AI services](https://lea
 rn.microsoft.com/azure/defender-for-cloud/ai-onboarding/?wt.mc_id=meetup_2
 6842_webpage_reactor)\n[Defender for Cloud - AI threat protection](https:/
 /learn.microsoft.com/azure/defender-for-cloud/ai-threat-protection/?wt.mc_
 id=meetup_26842_webpage_reactor)\n\n📌 This session is a part of a serie
 s! Learn more [**here**](https://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-
 1644/?wt.mc_id=meetup_S-1644_webpage_reactor)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/microsoft-reactor-toronto/events/3134
 04622/
