 ty on Azure DevOps (GHAzDO) is transforming application security for devel
 opment teams. In this exclusive webinar\, we'll explore how GHAzDO brings 
 GitHub's powerful security capabilities directly to your Azure DevOps work
 flows\, empowering teams to identify and fix vulnerabilities faster than e
 ver before.\n\nThis session is a part of a series! Learn more **[here](htt
 ps://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1311/?wt.mc_id=meetup_S-1311
